snippet.title: Disrupting Strategic Communications & Branding | The Disruptors Network | Amber Hurdle
snippet.description:
Welcome to the 12th episode of the Disruptors Network podcast. Amber Hurdle helps leaders confidently define and position their value so they can maximize their influence, focus, and results. As a dynamic professional speaker and CEO of Amber Hurdle
Consulting, a multi-award-winning talent optimization firm, and founder of the Velvet Machete Leadership Society, she pioneers using both science and marketing principles to strengthen brands and leaders from the inside out. We discuss branding, Amber's career, and what's to come.

Merch:
https://the-disruptors-network.myshopify.com/

Hosts:
Ralph DiBugnara: https://www.instagram.com/dibug/
Eulogio Medina: https://www.instagram.com/_whattagoodchoice/
Vicky Llerena: https://www.instagram.com/llerenavicky/ (Special Appearance)

Follow us on socials:
https://www.instagram.com/disruptorsnetwork/

Chapters:
0:00 Intro
2:30 Social Media and the Course of PR
6:10 Amber's Consumer Value Proposition
9:06 How to Work in Mature Industries
12:07 How Did you Get Into PR?
14:57 Challenging Project
21:04 You're Not Weak
29:19 Overcoming "Limitations"
33:40 Book Recommendations
36:16 Connecting with the Unknown
43:25 Outro
